author: Portable Professional
description: Totally agree that life is pretty much the same, and it’s easier on a lot of us as well are still able to work and used to being home. Feeling grateful, and yup... a little guilty to admit it! Thanks for sharing !

description: Don\'t feel guilty! This is our time to show others that we can prepare our lives in our own way and that it\'s not as risky as other think it is!

author: Eternal Summer Rising - Traveling Techies
description: I guess we are coping better as we are used to working in different locations or just inside the house, hotels or room. Staying at home this quarantine makes no difference except we don\'t have more stamps in our passports.
title: I guess we are coping better as we are used to working in different locations or just inside the house, hotels or room. Staying at home this quarantine makes no difference except we don\'t have more stamps in our passports.

author: Johnny FD
description: Exactly. If anything, it\'s a nice forced break for those who tend to travel too quickly or often without really ever getting into a productive routine.
title: Exactly. If anything, it\'s a nice forced break for those who tend to travel too quickly or often without really ever getting into a productive routine.
